    <item>
      <title>特朗普和经济增长担忧加剧南非政策不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/trump-growth-concerns-add-to-south-africa-policy-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项衡量南非对政府政策信心水平的指标显示，12 月份不确定性水平上升，反映出人们对经济复苏步伐以及美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普可能对全球贸易产生的影响的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/trump-growth-concerns-add-to-south-africa-policy-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
