      <title>华盛顿州最高警官认为有空间与特朗普团队合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/washington-attorney-general-sees-room-to-work-with-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿州新任司法部长尼克·布朗正准备与第二届特朗普政府展开一场高风险冲突，并誓言反击共和党在移民、堕胎和环境方面的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/washington-attorney-general-sees-room-to-work-with-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克称美国拨款法案是“犯罪”，激起共和党反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/us-government-funding-fight-previews-house-republican-turbulence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克敦促立法者关闭联邦政府，而不是接受众议院议长迈克·约翰逊达成的暂时资助运营的协议，这引发了国会共和党人的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/us-government-funding-fight-previews-house-republican-turbulence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:49:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥通过 2025 年预算，不上调房产税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/chicago-officials-approve-2025-budget-without-property-tax-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊取消了其提出的房产税上调提议后，芝加哥市议会批准了 2025 年约 170 亿美元的预算，其中征税和费用将增加 1.8 亿美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/chicago-officials-approve-2025-budget-without-property-tax-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 23:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
